						<summary>

						<p>This inscription refers to the gift of land for rebuilding the compound wall and installation of the deity Tiruttiyūrmuṭṭattu sōmaviḷāgamuḍaiya-nāyaṉār by Māḷava-chakravartti, who also gave some tax-free land.</p>						

